    @Deprecated
public class Duration
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Duration>, java.lang.Cloneable
    A duration is a scalar value paired with a unit of time. For example, 10 milliseconds and 50 minutes are both durations (scalar + unit of time).
